    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/08de1974aa04460007c2f4857fc6e95e.poster.avif?t=1751914943\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/08de1974aa04460007c2f4857fc6e95e.webm?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/08de1974aa04460007c2f4857fc6e95e.mp4?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>故事<br><br>宇宙有一种引发混乱和秩序的方式。阿马尔是这个世界痛苦的根源。你有力量通过它的试炼吗？加入 Amar 的旅程，更多地了解他自己、他的世界，以及生活的真正意义。看看成为如此多痛苦的根源却又被迫生活是什么感觉。让自己与这个世界的人们建立深厚的关系，共同解决生活中的问题。为了度过难关，我们必须了解彼此，了解我们真正想要的生活。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/efd3129570bf82a2f8984fe0a6940c75.poster.avif?t=1751914943\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/efd3129570bf82a2f8984fe0a6940c75.webm?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/efd3129570bf82a2f8984fe0a6940c75.mp4?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>战斗<br><br>Ex Angelus 以其高节奏的战斗优先考虑自己。冲刺和快速移动，躲避敌人的攻击。通过不断攻击并保持 Flow Gauge 高来推动你的攻击性。通过平衡你的耐力和使用你的系列电路能力将你的输出推到极限来管理你的伤害输出。深流潜水可以让你移动得如此之快，从而躲避敌人的攻击。如果流量计下降得太低，您将无法跟上！战斗的快感是唯一能让你在这些艰苦的战斗中活着的东西。你能处理吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/6dd042ae537750e839125145ddc2924c.poster.avif?t=1751914943\" width=366 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/6dd042ae537750e839125145ddc2924c.webm?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/6dd042ae537750e839125145ddc2924c.mp4?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>美妙的音乐和风景<br><br>Ex Angelus 让您惊叹于华丽的场景和美丽的背景。色彩和灯光将您带入一个值得探索的世界。音乐融合了动感和舒缓的氛围，以配合您在世界各地的步伐。有各种各样的谜题需要解决，有不同的部分可以搭建平台，你会发现这个世界充满挑战。这个世界有许多不同的探索途径，因此如果您想以自己的方式解决难题，您可以做出决定，因为前方有具有挑战性的敌人！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/32b9ce7316b40f740ff4f969e01dae17.poster.avif?t=1751914943\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/32b9ce7316b40f740ff4f969e01dae17.webm?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250510/extras/32b9ce7316b40f740ff4f969e01dae17.mp4?t=1751914943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
